{"id": 1466, "genre": 1001, "title": "你还挺烦哪一种“伸手党”的？", "description": "自己的事情要自己做，小时候的箴言忘了吗？（题图来自：Eline Van Dam ​​​​）", "record_count": 7761, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170120160121aebrU98pmMQ7kjs0.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-01-21T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 156928, "content": "他需要你帮忙的时候你随时随地能够联系上他 等你需要他的时候 他就如同死了一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898058}, {"id": 156929, "content": "要图的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 901163}, {"id": 159233, "content": "求赞党，群发党", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 918102}, {"id": 157186, "content": "求人做事尽力帮忙最后还被嫌弃的时候真的很想杀人?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 265554}, {"id": 157443, "content": "期末复习的时候明明自己翻翻书就可以找到答案或者解题思路的，就算再简单的题也非要问别人这道题怎么做!", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 891469}, {"id": 157189, "content": "明明不顺路 自己走二十分钟就到了还要别人送\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 909403}, {"id": 161541, "content": "百度一下就有的东西偏要我分享", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 924717}, {"id": 156934, "content": "明明答案能看懂，明明能问老师偏要问同学的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 912384}, {"id": 157190, "content": "把别人对自己的好当成天经地义的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 912960}, {"id": 165126, "content": "推荐电影一起看的时候非要剧透的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 932245}, {"id": 162311, "content": "好好学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 895728}, {"id": 156936, "content": "没事的时候不来找我，来找我的时候不是借钱就是没人陪", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 903108}, {"id": 157192, "content": "微博评论里各种求口红色号或者背景音乐什么的，拜托，你往下翻翻评论就有，飞得问博主吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 911144}, {"id": 156937, "content": "复制你的照片到朋友圈只用一秒钟", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 855060}, {"id": 157194, "content": "联系只为了利益", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 901517}, {"id": 159243, "content": "丢个邮箱要装修清单", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 918141}, {"id": 163595, "content": "有事儿才找你，每个问题间隔20分钟，每次问4个问题，过几一个星期又有新的问题要问了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 916067}, {"id": 156940, "content": "帮我设计个logo呗，随便弄下就好了", "image": null, "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 634998}, {"id": 157196, "content": "你帮我审下稿子，很快\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 883242}, {"id": 156942, "content": "上课直接拿别人文具用，还不说一声谢谢", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 537814}, {"id": 157198, "content": "刚认识就让你到哪去都给她带礼物，不好意思我们熟嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 744182}, {"id": 157966, "content": "作业不自己做就等着人做好啦然后抄，连自己百度都不会。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 914229}, {"id": 156944, "content": "曾经是学习群群管理。。现在是另外一个学习群成员。资料，干货 课程通知 课件文件作业什么的 群文件群公告写的清清楚楚，总有那么几个人在公屏问。神烦这种。找一下都不知道找，又不难，这都不会的话还学个鬼。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 40203}, {"id": 156946, "content": "Ta从不和你联系，一旦联系就是要红包……", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 912406}, {"id": 157459, "content": "把自己当弱者，觉得自己的事情别人都应该帮忙的人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 913733}, {"id": 157715, "content": "自己根本就不了解，也不尝试做一做就让别人帮他而自己却去打游戏的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 914108}, {"id": 162323, "content": "能跟她老公 非要跟我", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 926182}, {"id": 156948, "content": "借钱不还，我不是欠你的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 699020}, {"id": 165908, "content": "什么都要占点便宜的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 860276}, {"id": 156949, "content": "宿舍里借牙膏，借洗发膏，借晾衣架等等", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 120415}, {"id": 157205, "content": "有些朋友不过脑子我也就忍了，连眼睛都不过，有些答案明明已经写的清清楚楚，还要再三提问。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 905948}, {"id": 160021, "content": "脑残问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 781562}, {"id": 157206, "content": "一天到晚要demo，要你妹的demo，滚回去自己写！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 667141}, {"id": 157974, "content": "只有用到你的时候，他才认识你，平时招呼都不打", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 914787}, {"id": 157207, "content": "根本不熟的人很久不联系 突然让你给他发红包 懵逼脸 莫名其妙嘛 ?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 913016}, {"id": 158743, "content": "跪求", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 916867}, {"id": 156953, "content": "明明可以翻课本，非要问同学", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 907413}, {"id": 157209, "content": "教科书就有的答案还非得问别人，【摊手无语状】", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 904316}, {"id": 157977, "content": "上课自己不听课，到考试问一些特别基础浪费时间的题", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 769326}, {"id": 157210, "content": "首先得有人认识我，来到这个地球快20年。一个人都没见过", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 913040}, {"id": 160282, "content": "懒鬼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 920282}, {"id": 166682, "content": "盗图", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 685050}, {"id": 156955, "content": "直接粘贴你写的东西，却不和你说一声", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 911832},